  • public final class ImageType
extends NamedIconEntity
    Image type defines different images to use on on clusters, and include information needed by provisioners to provision machines from different providers.

      • getProviderMap

        public Map<String,Map<String,String>> getProviderMap()
        Get the provider map for this image type. The provider map has provider names as its keys, and a map of any key values needed by the provisioners given that provider. For example, all cloud providers require the 'image' key, which specifies which provider-specific image to use.
        Returns:
        Mapping of provider to data needed when provisioning nodes from the provider.
